---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Mit Freuden";
const description = "What brings joy to life? That's right: it's really, really well-made software. We think so too.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} locale="en">
  <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-12 text-gray-700">
    <div class="mb-24">
      <h1 class="page-title text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-gray-900 mb-6">Mit Freuden</h1>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl">
        What brings joy to life? That's right: it's really, <em>really</em> well-made software. We think so too.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Complete solutions that deliver on their promises</h2>

      <p>
        We develop <b>complete, ready-to-use software</b> together with you – from the initial idea to smooth production
        operation. Our solutions are web-based and run on all platforms. Including native mobile apps for iOS and Android
        if needed. This way you reach your users everywhere, without compromising on performance or user experience.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Software that brings joy</h2>

      <p>
        What good is the best technology if nobody enjoys working with it? Really, really good software must not only
        function, it should also <b>bring joy</b>. That's why we focus on intuitive usability and design that not only
        looks good, but enables simple and functional operation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Experience that moves industries</h2>

      <p>
        Our team has implemented projects in the most diverse sectors – from <b
          >retail to energy to warehouse logistics</b
        >. Every industry has its own challenges, and we know how to master them.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Future-proof through proven technology</h2>

      <p>
        We rely on <b>proven, future-proof technologies</b> that grow with your business. Our focus is on B2B solutions such
        as workflow automation, data visualization, or complex logistics systems that have been successfully deployed for
        years. We deliver software not only quickly and securely, but also scalably – from startups to enterprise solutions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">We are reliable partners</h2>

      <p>
        For us, software development is more than just writing code. We <b>live your projects</b> with you, understand your
        goals, and develop solutions that truly fit you. No standard packages, no half measures. Custom-built software that
        advances your business and brings you and your team joy day after day.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Sounds good?</h2>

      <p>Then let's talk. We look forward to your project.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
